          Our Learning Journey
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-100 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          From curiosity to creativity, we guide kids through a meaningful learning path — with play, purpose, and projects that spark growth.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center">
